ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This was my first ever film class, and it was definitely life-changing. It's just a fantastic class. Penny is amazing. The workload isn't too hard. The films are for the most part very good, and even when they're not amazing, the analysis is great. Take it if you have any interest in films or Italian.
